content:
Administering, Deploying, and Launching OmniScripts

Import, version, launch, and deploy OmniScripts. OmniScripts can be launched from Experience Cloud sites, object pages, Console Apps, and remote sites. They can be deployed to Salesforce sites and external services.

Managing OmniScripts
The following topics tell you how to manage your OmniScripts:
Deploying an OmniScript
Launch OmniScripts
Embed an OmniScript in Another OmniScript
Configuring Community Profiles for OmniScript

An OmniScript can be reused, versioned, modified, and activated without reconfiguring the page. It can be launched from Communities, Object detail pages, and Vlocity Card Actions.
title: Administering, Deploying, and Launching OmniScripts in Salesforce
